reviewText: Enjoyed this DVD.  It was entertaining.
excellent overview of Jackie  - - well worthwhile
Beautifully presented and well researched. I am the biggest Jackie fan ever -I also liked the fact that there was a CD.

This is a well done stroll through time with one of our former first ladies.  Since she was such a private person in the midst of tragic history, this memoir with her voice, from her perspective is informative and enchanting.  Well worth the purchase - watched it with one of my daughters
